name: Verify the Agency Number field is present under filter Edits Screen for Renewal reports

testSteps.description: 1: Verify the Agency Number field is present under filter Edits Screen for Renewal reports ({Reports=Upcoming Renewals})

children.description: Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And user Navigates to Reports
And select Renewals 'Renewals' from Reports
And select Reports 'Upcoming Renewals' from Renewals
When user navigates to the filter edits screen
Then the field 'Agency Number' column should not be displayed for the mentioned reports
And the field Agency Number should be displayed in Filter Edits

testSteps.description: 2: Verify the Agency Number field is present under filter Edits Screen for Renewal reports ({Reports=Renewals In Progress})
